Build instructions (Get your generator name by typing "cmake", a list of valid
ones is at the bottom of the help screen):

cd build
cmake .. -G "YOUR COOL GENERATOR NAME"
[your project files are in the build directory now]

Just as a sidenote, in order to build this project, you will need a version of
gcc that is greater than or equal to 4.5.0, or a version of msvc greater than
or equal to the 2010 version of the compiler.
